OL,3,GNorth East
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA dry and bright start to the
OL,6,Fweekend, sunshine turning hazy from
OL,7,Flate morning and clouding over further
OL,8,Fin the afternoon. Feeling warm,
OL,9,Falthough the breeze in places will
OL,10,Ftake the edge of the temperatures.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FStaying dry with clear spells
OL,13,Fdeveloping and the wind easing light
OL,14,Ffor most places. Mild in urban areas
OL,15,Fbut notably cooler in rural spots.
OL,16,
OL,17,CSunday:FAny cloud should dissipate
OL,18,Fthroughout the morning with plenty of
OL,19,Fsunshine during the afternoon, feeling
OL,20,Fwarm or very warm in places with
OL,21,Ftemperatures on the rise.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
