OL,3,GNorth East
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Monday to Wednesday:
OL,6,FSettled and warm with bright sunshine
OL,7,Ffor most on Monday. Expecting
OL,8,Ftemperatures to decrease Tuesday and
OL,9,FWednesday as the wind turns onshore
OL,10,Fbut remaining dry with variable
OL,11,Famounts of cloud.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
